PrecisEnactment of the POLLUTANT DISCHARGE REPORTING REGULATIONS, 1995 which require the master or owner of a ship or the operator of an oil handling facility to report any discharge or probable discharge of a marine pollutant to a Canadian pollution prevention officer or to an appropriate official of the nearest coastal state.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1995-0351 Publication Date: 1995-08-09
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the POLLUTANT DISCHARGE REPORTING REGULATIONS, 1995 which
require the master or owner of a ship or the operator of an oil handling
facility to report any discharge or probable discharge of a marine
pollutant to a Canadian pollution prevention officer or to an appropriate
official of the nearest coastal state.
